{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Croaker: A 2D Platformer. It may seem basic at first, but as you get deeper into the game, you realize that there's more features than your average platformer. There's 38 levels with 8 more coming soon, divided among 3 chapters. The lore slowly pieces together what's actually happening. There's more- Online leaderboards, built-in speedrun leaderboards, account saving and loading, Xbox controller support, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What's So Great:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s unique Platformer Level Editor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/Level_Editor.png?t=1737345527\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Leaderboards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/leaderboards.png?t=1737345527\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">50 Different Levels!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/Screenshot_2024-12-21_155747.png?t=1737345527\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/levels.png?t=1737345527\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speedrunning Mechanics<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/speedrunning.png?t=1737345527\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12 skins, purchasable with Apples (The Frog, Jeremy has 4 variants and Pink Man has 2)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/shop.png?t=1737345527\" /><br>Holiday Themes<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/Screenshot_2024-12-21_155747.png?t=1737345527\" /><br>In Game + Steam achievements!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/achievements.png?t=1737345527\" /><br>Integrated Save and Load System! (Apples and Speedrun Times are automatically recorded.)<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2920070/extras/save_and_load.png?t=1737345527\" /><br>Since this is an Indie Game with no real playtesters, it is very easy for me to release the game without doing a thorough check for bugs. <strong>That said, if there are any bugs, please report them under \u201cOnline -&gt; Bug Reporting\u201d.</strong> The good thing about this is that there are frequent updates to the game. Typically, on weekends, I will check the bug list and make updates to the game based off of this information. If there\u2019s nothing there, I just go off of bugs that I know exist. <strong>Sometimes, huge content drops can happen during these updates!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;it's a <strong>game</strong> alright&quot; -Milkman Timby, Composer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;made me dissolve into <strong>hydrogen atoms</strong>&quot; -funkedt0ast, Artist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<strong>frog&quot;</strong>- Botscoutt, Playtester</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"ouch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2920070/0e9fedf3af97de538a0d1e6037e54568163322e2.jpg"},{"name":"Am I a Billionaire yet?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2920070/69d07d211d860b96ab472717f989d1d671fed665.jpg"},{"name":"I have at least 1 apple","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2920070/e1cfc7e4a7a698b583bd98dd8f0fe8a79bd7018b.jpg"},{"name":"i am a profession